Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Mrs. Nakajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, about your ad for a tutor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I have no intention of going to Yasogami High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that no one else could start tutoring right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I was just looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:03:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}August 10th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When a friend learned he was tutoring,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he asked Narukami Yu to help out at the daycare center.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He had no way of knowing that these simple tasks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}would lead to new hardships.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuta broke my Neo Featherman robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not broken! Lemme see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't fight—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I expect you to compensate for the toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I warm your dinner up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nanako. Have you heard of Neo Featherman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everyone loves him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Heroes these days are something else, aren't they?
