Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may have solved the case, but watch the booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't a chick, what's keeping you out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fox asked me to pick up a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's put me through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when were you such a tease?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, that was a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
