Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do this and—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuuta said he saw Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did! I really saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Loveline only exists in the TV.
