Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Hell in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Teddie! What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should act like Teddie and hightail it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What a weird bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not a suspicious bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't his voice sound off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's all stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it doesn't seem natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's normally more, uh, hyperactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how he randomly rolls around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why'd he run from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie's got it bear-y tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}August 17th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After learning the hardships of labor and the life of Teddie,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Narukami Yu has grown a little more mature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's no time for rest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really cloudy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earning money is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief! Someone catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She apparently hit her head when the thief pushed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't look serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my, aren't you cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go hit the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've got work.{bitch, please}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'll be out late, so you two can eat without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro said he'd be home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is school fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It isn't fun for me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always surrounded by idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}August 18th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summer vacation is halfway over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his interactions with the people around him are beginning to change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're that boy from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you coming to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going to visit that elderly woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for an in-patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly forward.{wow, what a whore}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand being a nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old farts are bossy, and the men leer at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone always leaves me as soon as they recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's good they get discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should quit my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, let's put that aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's going to be a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can breeze through it with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my number, so give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell like alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the daycare center.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I found a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Yuuta isn't really my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's from my husband's old marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm still so unsure of how to act around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he hates me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just relax by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to be moving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town holds too many memories of my late husband for me to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband gave it to me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My love for him had dried up there at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no point in hanging onto those old memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I met you here in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the spitting image of my husband in his younger years.
