Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1.5\pos(652,660)}This indomitable fishing pole will never break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}With this, you'll only need one line and hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Call now, and we'll throw in a set of fishing gear—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a delivery here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out!
