Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}August 20th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yu Narukami's summer vacation is finally reaching its climax.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}You've got some major bags under your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wow! I wanna eat some shaved ice!{background Teddie}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}Isn't Nanako with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um, all of them!{teddy}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}My uncle's bringing her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}I had a feeling we'd run into each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}I want to give you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}That's my... But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it mean a lot to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed really sad after you threw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy when my husband gave this to me that I couldn't see his face through all my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I truly loved my husband, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in class was promising they'd watch the fireworks together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one invited me to tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's just jealous of me because they're stupid!{haha what a dumb fuck}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, no one gets fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put everyone out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed a picture in your room that said today is your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you choose this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a game you can't play by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to ask someone to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone's so goofy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun goofing off with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I need a toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's what you get for eating so much shaved ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, I stole the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Yuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids with moms like this always turn out rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is about what I'd expect from a failure of a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She's bleeding bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, help her. Please help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.64,signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAs seen on TV\fs65\frz347.377\bord0\blur0.6\c&HF3F2EE&\pos(678,314)}Narukami Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, I didn't think he'd actually call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's bleeding from the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, bandage the wound with a long piece of material.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something long...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebi, I need to borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to keep it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, but we're out of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Daddy. I want that big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. You're the first person to go all-out like this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Told ya she's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure weren't, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might've lost sight of what really matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saving lives truly is wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I forgot something so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you helped me remember. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me regain my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall cherish them this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Amagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm with her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to walk in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, you're so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if you get sick again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we took so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a while getting everyone dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lookin' good! Lookin' real good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Thanks for taking care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle, didn't you have work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I dumped it on Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't pass up on the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave me some cotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, why don't we go hit up a shooting booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nighttime at a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A couple leans up against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unaccustomed to wearing a yukata, it spills open.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sudden monologue?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for us to couple up and enjoy the sights!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I agree with Teddie!
